reviewText:
good if u want to learn mas oyama karate.i was expecting to learn more
sparring drills n tec not so much forms. but if u want to learn form this is a
good purchases for u

This is an excellent collection of videos, I practice Kyokushin and has been very useful as an adjunct to learn and correct (techniques, kata, movements, etc.). Of course, who better to Kancho Matsui for these videos?.

Ossu!
